  "description": "<i>Hugo: The Evil Mirror</i> is a 3D platform game starring Hugo the TV trolls children, Trollerit, Trollerat, and Trollerut. Scylla the evil witch has captured Hugo in a magical mirror, before the eyes of his children. Afterwards the mirror is split in three pieces and scattered around Troll forest. Now each of the children has to recover a piece of the mirror to release their father from it.<br><br>Gameplay includes sled racing, platforming, defeating enemies and collecting diamonds. You play as each of the three children to retrieve a piece of the mirror. If all pieces are retrieved you enter the mirror where you play as Hugo who has to free himself by taking on Scyllas projection inside the mirror.",
